            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Il <rs key="#Bishops">vescovo</rs> di <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Bishops">Lucca</placeName>
                        <persName ref="#people/213" key="#Bishops">Pietro</persName> siede in
                        giudizio intus <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/72"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> beatissime Sancte Marie Dei
                            getrix</orgName> ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/63" key="#Churches"
                            >ad Monte</placeName>. Assistono i preti Tassilo del fu Andrea,
                        Teupaldo, Teudimundo, <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Adalmarius"
                                >Adalmari</name></persName>, altro Teupaldo, <persName
                            key="#Priests"><name ref="Liutbaldus">Liupaldo</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Iohannes"
                        >Giovanni</name></persName>, Ghisolfo, Savino, il diacono Teobaldo. Si
                        presenta da una parte il <rs key="#Priests">prete e visdomino</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Viventius">Vivenzio</name></persName>
                        del <persName>fu <name ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName>, dall’altra il
                            <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Stefanus">Stefano</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildiprando</name></persName>, in
                        lite fra loro: secondo il visdomino, il prete entrò nella <orgName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/264"><rs
                                key="#Baptismal_churches">pieve</rs> di Sant’Ippolito sita loco
                                <placeName ref="#places/152" key="#Baptismal_churches"
                                >Anniani</placeName></orgName> e sottrasse fruges malo ordinem; il
                        prete si difende asserendo di essere stato ordinato e confermato rettore e
                        custode nella stessa chiesa; il visdomino contraddice quest’ultima
                        affermazione. Il prete Ghisperto interroga il prete, domandando se può
                        provare la sua affermazione con testimoni; avuta risposta affermativa,
                        ricevute le dovute garanzie dai due contendenti, convoca, quarto die, il <rs
                            key="#Assembly">placito</rs>, in seguito al quale lo stesso vescovo fa
                        adscire il prete. Scrive la pagina il <rs key="#Writer #Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Priests"><name ref="Ildebertus"
                            >Ildiperto</name></persName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                        sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Tassilo"
                                >Tassilo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> del <persName>fu <name ref="Andreas"
                                >Andrea</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Teudemundus">Teudimundo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Teobaldus">Teupaldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Savinus">Savino</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Gisbertus">Ghisperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Teobaldus">Teupaldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Deacons"><name
                                ref="Teobaldus">Teobaldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
